src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Simple membre, je ne fais rien</p><ol><li><p>Statut matrimonial&nbsp;:</p></li></ol><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p>Célibataire</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> marié (e)</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Divorcé (e)</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Séparé (e)</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Union libre</p><ol><li><p>Niveau d’étude<em>.</em></p></li></ol><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Primaire</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Secondaire</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Professionnel</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Universitaire</p><ol><li><p>Nombre d’année à l’Église Évangélique de Nazon</p></li></ol><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Moins de 2 ans</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> 2–5 ans</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> 6–10 ans</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Plus de 10 ans</p><p><strong>SECTION 2 : Perception du mentorat dans l’Église</strong></p><ol><li><p>Avez-vous déjà entendu parler du concept de mentorat chrétien ?</p></li></ol><p>Oui</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Non</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><ol><li><p>Selon vous, le mentorat consiste principalement à faire quoi&nbsp;? (Vous pouvez choisir plusieurs réponses)</p></li></ol><ul><li><p>Former des personnes (disciples) capables d'impacter la communauté à travers l'église&nbsp;;</p></li></ul><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Enseigner la Parole de Dieu par l'exemple&nbsp;;</p><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Guider moralement et spirituellement&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Créer un lien de fraternité et d’écoute&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Assurer la continuité de la vision de la communauté</p><ol><li><p>Selon vous, y a-t-il actuellement un programme structuré de mentorat dans l’EEN ?</p></li></ol><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Oui</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Non</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Je ne sais pas s'il y en a</p><ol><li><p>Si non, comment décririez-vous l’accompagnement socio-spirituel actuel dans l’Église ?</p></li></ol><p><em>Cochez toutes les réponses qui s'appliquent.</em></p><p>Informel et spontané&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Réservé aux anciens&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Centré sur la prédication et école dominicale seulement&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Je ne remarque pas de système d’accompagnement de mentorat</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p><strong>SECTION 3 : Expérience personnelle du mentorat et besoins de formation.</strong></p><ol><li><p>Avez-vous déjà bénéﬁcié d’un accompagnement personnel (spirituel, moral ou ministériel) par le mentorat dans votre Église ?</p></li></ol><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Oui</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Non</p><p>Si oui, par qui ?</p><p>Pasteur&nbsp;; Diacre&nbsp;; Responsable de l'école du dimanche&nbsp;; Leader de la jeunesse</p><ol><li><p>Cet accompagnement a-t-il eu un impact positif sur votre croissance spirituelle ?</p></li></ol><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Oui, beaucoup&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Oui, un peu&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Pas vraiment&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Pas du tout</p><ol><li><p>Que Pensez-vous que l'absence de mentorat structuré affecte ?</p></li></ol><p><em>Cochez toutes les réponses qui s'appliquent, pas plus que deux.</em></p><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> La formation des nouveaux convertis, ils se laissent seuls&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> La relève des leaders capables&nbsp;;</p><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> L’unité et la cohésion communautaire&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> La ﬁdélité et la motivation des membres</p><ol><li><p>Dans quels domaines estimez-vous qu'une pratique du mentorat serait le plus utile</p></li></ol><p>? (Choisissez jusqu’à trois)</p><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Formation spirituelle&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Formation au leadership&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Soutien moral et relationnel&nbsp;;</p><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Accompagnement des jeunes&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAACQAAAAkCAYAAADhAJiYAAAABmJLR0QA/wD/AP+gvaeTAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAYUlEQVRYhe3YoRGAQAwF0RxDkygcPYECA2Ue6hCYlYnYpyJ3vkzbz7tHIVN2wN88jm1dWmbIcT09ouBCBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRAwiBhGDiEHEIGIQMYgYRL7/0PjPZCu30Asj7goLDG6BSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Suivi des nouveaux convertis</p><ol><li><p>Selon vous, quel est le plus grand obstacle à la mise en place d’un programme de mentorat à l’Église Évangélique de Nazon ?</p></li></ol><p></p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Manque de vision claire&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Manque de mentors formés&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Manque d’intérêt des membres&nbsp;;</p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="100%" height="auto" display="block" margin="2rem auto" style="float: none; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 10px 20px; cursor: nwse-resize;"><p> Manque de temps / d’organisation</p><ol><li><p>Seriez-vous favorable à la mise en place d’un programme oﬃciel de mentorat spirituel dans l’Église ?</p></li></ol><p>Oui&nbsp;; Non&nbsp;; Pas d'opinion</p><p></p><ol><li><p>Souhaitez-vous personnellement être formé(e) pour devenir mentor à l’avenir ?</p></li></ol><p>Oui Non Peut-être oui</p><h2>Bibliographie/Webographie</h2><p>Adventiste Magazine. « <em>Nous avons tous besoin d’un mentor ».</em> 2023.<br><a target="_new" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://adventistemagazine.com/nous-avons-tous-besoin-dun-mentor/">https://adventistemagazine.com/nous-avons-tous-besoin-dun-mentor/</a>.</p><p>Arnold, Johann Christoph Heinrich. <em>Guide du leader pour le discipulat</em>. Paris : Communauté de Bruderhof, 2001.</p><p>Bible. <em>La Sainte Bible</em>. Version Louis Segond 1910. Paris : Société Biblique Française.</p><p>Bourdieu, Pierre. <em>Raisons pratiques : Sur la théorie de l’action</em>. Paris : Éditions du Seuil, 1994.</p><p>Brady, Chris, et Orrin Woodward. <em>Lancer une révolution en leadership</em>. Paris : Éditions du Leadership, 2015.</p><p>Calvin, Jean. <em>Institution de la religion chrétienne</em>. Paris : Kerygma, 2009.</p><p>Cogan, Mordechai, et Hayim Tadmor. <em>II Kings: A New Translation with Introduction and Commentary</em>. Anchor Yale Bible. New Haven, CT : Yale University Press, 1988.</p><p>Cole, Neil. <em>Une Bible, du café… des disciples : Vers une multiplication de disciples</em>. Charols : Éditions Impact, 2007.</p><p>Factorial. « <em>Le mentorat en entreprise, un levier de croissance pour les collaborateurs comme pour l’entreprise</em> ». Blog RH Factorial, 2023.<br><a target="_new" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://factorial.fr/blog/mentorat-entreprise/">https://factorial.fr/blog/mentorat-entreprise/</a>.</p><p>Foster, Richard J. <em>La célébration de la discipline : Le chemin de la croissance spirituelle</em>. Traduit de l’anglais. Charols : Excelsis, 2010.</p><p>Gray, John, et Thomas Hobbs. <em>A Critical and Exegetical Commentary on the Book of Kings</em>. Edinburgh : T&amp;T Clark, 1970. Consulté le 23 décembre 2025.<br><a target="_new" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://soniclight.com/tcon/notes/pdf/2kings.pdf">https://soniclight.com/tcon/notes/pdf/2kings.pdf</a>.</p><p>Henry, Matthew. <em>Commentaire biblique complet</em>. Vol. 1. Charols : Excelsis, 1998.</p><p>House, Paul R. <em>1, 2 Kings</em>. New American Commentary. Nashville, TN : B&amp;H Publishing Group, 1995.</p><p>Hyatt, Michael. <em>Être un leader visionnaire</em>. Paris : Éditions Un Monde Différent, 2013.</p><p>Keil, Carl Friedrich, et Franz Delitzsch. <em>Biblical Commentary on the Old Testament</em>. Vol. 3. Edinburgh : T&amp;T Clark, 1866–1891. Consulté le 10 janvier 2026.<br><a target="_new" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://archive.org/details/biblicalcommenta03keil03">https://archive.org/details/biblicalcommenta03keil03</a>.</p><p>Keil, Carl Friedrich, et Franz Delitzsch. <em>Commentary on the Old Testament</em>. Vol. 3. Peabody, MA : Hendrickson Publishers, 2006.</p><p>Luther, Martin. <em>Le Notre Père expliqué aux chrétiens</em>. Traduit de l’allemand. Paris : Éditions Olivétan, 2016.</p><p>MacArthur, John. <em>The MacArthur Bible Commentary</em>. Nashville, TN : Thomas Nelson, 2005.</p><p>Malidor, Philippe. « La place de la croix dans le mentorat ». <em>Cahiers de l’École Pastorale</em>. Croire Publications, 2022.<br><a target="_new" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.croirepublications.com/cahiers-ecole-pastorale/l-accompagnement-et-l-ecoute/article/la-place-de-la-croix-dans-le-mentorat">https://www.croirepublications.com/cahiers-ecole-pastorale/l-accompagnement-et-l-ecoute/article/la-place-de-la-croix-dans-le-mentorat</a>.</p><p>Miles, Matthew B., et A. Michael Huberman. <em>Qualitative Data Analysis: A Sourcebook of New Methods</em>. 2ᵉ éd. Thousand Oaks, CA : Sage Publications, 1994.</p><p>Mouvement des entreprises de France (MEDEF). <em>Guide du mentorat 2023</em>. Paris : MEDEF, 2023.<br><a target="_new" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.medef.com/uploads/media/default/0020/03/15781-guide-mentorat-2023-medef.pdf">https://www.medef.com/uploads/media/default/0020/03/15781-guide-mentorat-2023-medef.pdf</a>.</p><p>Munroe, Myles. <em>Devenir un leader</em>. Miami: Whitaker House, 2007.</p><p>Munroe, Myles. <em>L’Esprit du leadership</em>. Miami: Whitaker House, 2005.</p><p>Munroe, Myles. <em>Le pouvoir du caractère dans le leadership</em>. Miami: Whitaker House, 2006.</p><p>Rodriguez, M. R., et J. A. Williams. « Le mentorat : une exigence biblique et pratique pour le développement du leadership chrétien ». <em>Journal of Adventist Education</em> 85, no. 2 (2023). Consulté le 15 décembre 2025.<br><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.journalofadventisteducation.org/fr/2023.85.2.3">https://www.journalofadventisteducation.org/fr/2023.85.2.3</a>.</p><p>Stott, John. <em>La prédication apostolique</em>. Charols : Éditions Excelsis, 2011.</p><p>Université TÉLUQ. « <em>Mentorat en milieu éducatif</em> ». <em>WikiTEDia</em>, 2023. Consulté le 11 novembre 2025.<br><a target="_new" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://wiki.teluq.ca/wikitedia/index.php/Mentorat_en_milieu_%C3%A9ducatif">https://wiki.teluq.ca/wikitedia/index.php/Mentorat_en_milieu_%C3%A9ducatif</a>.</p><p>Von Rad, Gerhard. <em>La Genèse</em>. Commentaire de l’Ancien Testament. Genève : Labor et Fides, 1987.</p><p>Willard, Dallas. <em>L’esprit des disciplines</em>. Charols : Éditions Impact, 1999.</p><p>Willard, Dallas. <em>La rénovation du cœur</em>. Charols : Éditions Excelsis, 2009.</p><p>Woodward, Orrin. <em>Le mentorat, c’est important</em>. Paris : Éditions Leadership International, 2012.</p><p>Wikipédia. « Structure ». Consulté le 15 décembre 2025.<br><a target="_new" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Structure">https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Structure</a>.</p><p></p><h2>Biographie</h2><p>John Abda Tchargua Briny PHILIZAIRE est né en 1989 aux Abricots, dans la Grand’Anse, au sein d’une famille chrétienne de sept (7) enfants où il occupe la troisième place et est le premier garçon. L’environnement familial, fortement imprégné de valeurs morales et éducatives, a contribué à façonner son sens du devoir, sa discipline personnelle et son engagement envers la communauté dès son jeune âge.</p><p>Il est titulaire d’une Licence en Génie civil obtenue au Centre Universitaire Polytechnique d’Haïti (CUPH), avec une spécialisation en Béton Armé (BA). Cette formation lui a permis d’acquérir des compétences techniques en conception d’ouvrages, en calcul structurel et en gestion de projets de construction. Complété par d’autre étude en informatique bureautique au Centre Pilote Formation Professionnelle (CPFP), renforçant ainsi sa maîtrise des outils numériques et des systèmes de gestion documentaire.</p><p>En plus de sa formation technique, il est mémorant pour une licence en théologie au Séminaire de Théologie Évangélique de Port-au-Prince (STEP), orientées vers la réflexion théologique, l’ecclésiologie pratique et le leadership chrétien. Il est activement impliqué dans la vie ecclésiale comme responsable de plusieurs ministères à l’Église Évangélique de Nazon et occupe également une fonction de conseiller au sein du comité exécutif de la FAJ-UEBH, témoignant d’un engagement institutionnel et spirituel significatif.</p><p>Marié et père d’un garçon, il présente un profil alliant formation technique et engagement théologique, avec un intérêt particulier pour la promotion d’un leadership visionnaire et transmissible, fondé sur la responsabilité, la formation continue et l’accompagnement intentionnel des générations montantes au sein des communautés chrétiennes et des organisations associatives.</p><ol><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://mentorshow.com/blog/apprentissage-social-albert-bandura">https://mentorshow.com/blog/apprentissage-social-albert-bandura</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-1">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="http://www.sietmanagement.fr/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Capitalsocial">http://www.sietmanagement.fr/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Capitalsocial</a>. <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-2">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Impact_social">https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Impact_social</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-3">↑</a></p></li><li><p>Miles, M. B., &amp; Huberman, A. M. <em>Qualitative Data Analysis</em>. P.65 <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-4">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mentorat">https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mentorat</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-5">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Structure">https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Structure</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-6">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://factorial.fr/blog/mentorat%20entreprise/#:~:text=Le%20mentorat%20en%20entreprise%2C%20c,ou%20la%20mentor%C3%A9(e)">https://factorial.fr/blog/mentorat entreprise/#:~:text=Le%20mentorat%20en%20entreprise%2C%20c,ou%20la%20mentor%C3%A9(e)</a>. <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-7">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.medef.com/uploads/media/default/0020/03/15781-guide-mentorat-2023-medef.p">https://www.medef.com/uploads/media/default/0020/03/15781-guide-mentorat-2023-medef.</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-8">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.medef.com/uploads/media/default/0020/03/15781-guide-mentorat-2023-medef.pdf">https://www.medef.com/uploads/media/default/0020/03/15781-guide-mentorat-2023-medef.</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-9">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://wiki.teluq.ca/wikitedia/index.php/Mentorat_en_milieu_%C3%A9ducatif">https://wiki.teluq.ca/wikitedia/index.php/Mentorat_en_milieu_%C3%A9ducatif</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-10">↑</a></p></li><li><p>Myles Munroe, <em>L'Esprit du Leadership</em>, P. 45 <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-11">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.croirepublications.com/cahiers-ecole-pastorale/l-accompagnement-et-l-ecoute/article/la-place-de-la-croix-dans-le-mentorat">https://www.croirepublications.com/cahiers-ecole-pastorale/l-accompagnement-et-l-ecoute/article/la-place-de-la-croix-dans-le-mentorat</a>, 2019 <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-12">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.google.com/search?q=Analyse+ex%C3%A9g%C3%A9tique+de+Exode+33%3A11&amp;rlz=1C1RXQR_enHT1100HT1102&amp;oq=Analyse+ex%C3%A9g%C3%A9tique+de+Exode+33%3A11&amp;gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIHCAEQIRiPAjIHCAIQIRiPAtIBCjIzMzEyajBqMTWoAgiwAgHxBTXvNmLNf8oE8QU17zZizX_KBA&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8">https://www.google.com/search?q=Analyse+ex%C3%A9g%C3%A9tique+de+Exode+33%3A11&amp;rlz=1C1RXQR_enHT1100HT1102&amp;oq=Analyse+ex%C3%A9g%C3%A9tique+de+Exode+33%3A11&amp;gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIHCAEQIRiPAjIHCAIQIRiPAtIBCjIzMzEyajBqMTWoAgiwAgHxBTXvNmLNf8oE8QU17zZizX_KBA&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-13">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://archive.org/details/biblicalcommenta03keil03">https://archive.org/details/biblicalcommenta03keil03</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-14">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://soniclight.com/tcon/notes/pdf/2kings.pdf">https://soniclight.com/tcon/notes/pdf/2kings.pdf</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-15">↑</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://mentorshow.com/blog/apprentissage-social-albert-bandura">https://cdn.bookey.app/files/pdf/book/fr/l'esprit-des-disciplines.pdf</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="#footnote-ref-16">↑</a></p></li></ol><p></p>	[]	[]	2026-04-11 01:40:25.324+00	2026-04-17 19:10:58.997+00
